11
00:01:00,758 --> 00:01:02,925
Buy oranges!

12
00:01:03,590 --> 00:01:05,175
"Lord Ram."

13
00:01:05,673 --> 00:01:07,840
Let me go, sir.
I don't know.

14
00:01:10,370 --> 00:01:11,493
